OL,3,CBoy, 3, suffered vomiting and
OL,4,Cdiarrhoea after 'sewage release' on
OL,5,Cbeach
OL,7,FPauline says she believes the sickness
OL,8,Fwas linked to a sewage spill, but
OL,9,Fthere are a number of reasons why
OL,10,Fsomebody can become ill after swimming
OL,11,Fin the sea or being at the beach, such
OL,12,Fas agricultural run-off, animal faeces
OL,13,For simply swallowing too much seawater.
OL,15,FPauline said: "We hadn't been living
OL,16,Fhere that long. Myself and another
OL,17,Fneighbour, her little boy and my
OL,18,Flittle boy went down to the beach.
