OL,7,F"The boys dug in the sand, they got
OL,8,Ftheir hands all mucky, and that
OL,9,Fevening he was really poorly in bed.
OL,11,F"We went to the doctors, they just
OL,12,Fsaid he had a bit of sickness and
OL,13,Fdiarrhoea which should pass within a
OL,14,Fcouple of days.
OL,16,F"But the little boy down the road also
OL,17,Fhad the same thing exactly the same
OL,18,Ftime.
