OL,7,F"It just made me feel a bit sick to my
OL,8,Fstomach, thinking I'd let him play
OL,9,Faround in something that had been
OL,10,Fmaybe contaminated with effluent and
OL,11,FGod knows what else."
OL,13,FPauline says she wrote to her local MP
OL,14,Fand contacted .
OL,16,F"It made me really angry. It does put
OL,17,Fme off a little bit, which is a bit
OL,18,Fsad.
