OL,7,F"When we were down at the beach, there
OL,8,Fwere people swimming in the sea while
OL,9,Fthe discharge was happening, and I'm
OL,10,F100% sure they had no idea."
OL,12,FA spokesman for South West Water said:
OL,13,F"We care about our 860m of coastline,
OL,14,Four regions 100% bathing water
OL,15,Fquality, which we have successfully
OL,16,Fmaintained for three consecutive years
OL,17,Fand protecting the environment now and
OL,18,Fin the future.
