OL,7,F"We were one of the first water
OL,8,Fcompanies to have all our storm
OL,9,Foverflows monitored meaning we know
OL,10,Fexactly what is happening, when and
OL,11,Fwhere, allowing us to target
OL,12,Finvestment and make changes where it
OL,13,Fmatters most.
OL,15,F"We are serious about tackling storm
OL,16,Foverflows and change of this scale
OL,17,Ftakes time, ambition, and increased
OL,18,Finvestment ` and that is why we are
OL,19,Finvesting #850m in our region over 2
OL,20,Fyears.
