OL,5,Cbeach
OL,7,F"The increase in the storm overflow
OL,8,Fspills this year can be accounted for
OL,9,Fby the amount of named storms and
OL,10,Fweather warnings in 2023. It's clear
OL,11,Fwe need to redesign our systems, which
OL,12,Fwe are already doing.
OL,14,F"We will also be the first water
OL,15,Fcompany to meet the Government target
OL,16,Fof less than 10 spills per overflow,
OL,17,Fper year ` a decade ahead of target."
