OL,7,FKirsty Davies, from Surfers Against
OL,8,FSewage, said: "The water companies
OL,9,Fhave known about this for years.
OL,10,FThey've known there is climate change
OL,11,Fand an increase in extreme weather.
OL,13,F"Water companies now need to invest
OL,14,Fand address these issues. They are
OL,15,Fcurrently planning their five-year
OL,16,Fbusiness plan. They've got an
OL,17,Fopportunity now to start progressing
OL,18,Fand making change."
