OL,7,FLuke Pollard, Labour MP for Plymouth
OL,8,FSutton and Devonport, said: "We've got
OL,9,Fto get to grips with this because the
OL,10,Famount of raw human effluent being
OL,11,Fpumped into our natural environment is
OL,12,Foften utterly disgusting. That's why
OL,13,Fwe need stronger action than the
OL,14,FGovernment is taking today."
OL,16,FEnvironment Agency director of water
OL,17,FHelen Wakeham said: "Whilst it is
OL,18,Fdisappointing that water companies
OL,19,Fhave reported an increase in sewage
OL,20,Fspills in 2023, it is sadly not
OL,21,Fsurprising.
