OL,7,F"We demanded that 100 per cent of
OL,8,Foverflows were monitored by the end of
OL,9,Flast year as part of our drive to
OL,10,Fimprove transparency.
OL,12,F"Today's data shows water companies
OL,13,Fmust go further and faster to tackle
OL,14,Fstorm overflows and clean up our
OL,15,Fprecious waterways. We will be
OL,16,Fensuring the Environment Agency
OL,17,Fclosely scrutinise these findings and
OL,18,Ftake enforcement action where
OL,19,Fnecessary."
